T1  - Reconsidering the Relationship between Inflation and Relative Price Variability
AU  - CHOI, CHI-YOUNG
Y1  - 2010/08/01
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1538-4616.2010.00307.x
T2  - Journal of Money, Credit and Banking
